{"tid":1381931,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"728前線 想係度做檢討","createTime":"2019-07-29T10:53:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T11:19:19.000Z","uid":18824,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5ce26e43c4922123616d94a024fcba33df702c83","tid":1381931,"uid":18824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T10:53:22.000Z","msg":"速🐶一出，拉左39個，而我差少少係第40個，掙扎出翻去個人物件全部冇晒，真係唔想再發生呢啲嘢。以下好多係我個人意見<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">通訊</div></span><br />\n問題<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />現場訊息混亂，難以聯絡附近嘅戰線，好多人好驚內街失手就會被包圍<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔知前線退唔退，尋日前線係後面嘅人退就會退，而且想搵一個有利嘅地方守<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我試過跑去隔離戰線，拎手足contact，一旦隔離失守就叫佢即刻打俾我。效率唔高，同埋需要個人嘅對情況評估<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />前線同後排可以聯絡，用walkie <br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">坦克</span></div><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔夠裝，前線甚至有啲盾<span style=\"color: red;\">只係浮板</span>，而且難以組成盾陣<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">矛手<br />\n</div></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />尋日見到有人送咗啲竹上嚟，麻煩第2排嘅人拎住啲竹，參考長矛陣，咁樣對方指揮官就唔會貿貿然出動速🐶<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">弓手</span></div><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />lazer係好有用，但問題最前線有時開遮會擋住<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">法師 重要</span></span></div><br />\n當日打機搵左6個法師<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />準備時間有啲長，因為未必可以點燃到紙巾<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />火魔法範圍有啲細<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />紙皮加咗火水有啲難燒着<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />需要同坦克有更多溝通<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">障礙物防線</span></div><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />被反覆推進後，難以快速重組防線<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />用火去整防線係好有用，<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">真係唔好整息啲火</span>，出動速龍拉到咁多人係因為冇障礙物擋住佢哋。<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">速🐶應對</span></div><br />\n其實速🐶一出動，我哋就會<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">恐慌性逃走</span></span>，嗰種恐懼係好似遇溺咁樣，好難可以做到理性思考同埋反擊<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">🐶煙</span></div><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />尋日有人搵到消防喉出嚟，一下就搞掂啲煙<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />近距離嘅白煙係冇人頂到，除非個個都有60026<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">後退</span></div><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />尋日有手足落油，呢點真係好好<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲可以試吓波子，釘葵，老鼠膠<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">缺乏嘅職業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></span><br />\n1.訊息發放員，帶着大聲公，危急嗰陣可以理性思考，良好溝通能力，記得係要講事實唔係意見<br />\n2.溝通員，都係需要大聲公，促進前線達成去向嘅共識<br />\n3.弓手<br />\n4.法師<br />\n5.長予手<br />\n6.旗手<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">缺乏嘅物資</div></span><br />\n1.walkie，去到現場搵返個Channel就得<br />\n2.長盾"},{"pid":"d017977253de336806a3d9eebc5abb154fc06ad9","tid":1381931,"uid":229019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T10:56:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NX7EMKA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNX7EMKA.jpg&h=990f4b2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aEiXypB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaEiXypB.jpg&h=020f3ad0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ans9pwg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAns9pwg.png&h=b8d6d814&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"996a47175313e7468bed822a5e047325ec195867","tid":1381931,"uid":18824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T11:01:10.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b943e913577da55cf309bf4a3ce2c8d34ad51140","tid":1381931,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"996a47175313e7468bed822a5e047325ec195867","tid":1381931,"uid":18824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T11:01:10.000Z","msg":"push"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T11:02:00.000Z","msg":"你係發夢上前線咋<br />\n唔係真架 真既話就有人搵你架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7101bf72b06da61c36e648d779f8f23bab1d1eb3","tid":1381931,"uid":18824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T11:19:19.000Z","msg":"pushh"}]}